"1 1/2 tablespoons sugar","1/4 cup plus 2 tablespoons rice wine vinegar, divided","1 cup thinly shaved carrot","1 cup thinly shaved daikon radish","1/2 cup fresh cilantro leaves","2 tablespoons hoisin sauce","1 tablespoon soy sauce","1 tablespoon finely chopped green onion","2 teaspoons minced fresh ginger","1 teaspoon minced garlic","1 pound ground pork","1 tablespoon butter, melted","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  Cooking spray","4  hamburger buns, split horizontally"